{"tid":732032,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[改歌]龍珠超「究極の聖戦バトル」粵語中文版","createTime":"2018-07-06T16:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T18:28:57.000Z","uid":14503,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"17b7cb190bb3102a9dedc7ac872aa68dff93d284","tid":732032,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:27:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dwmz0vxLJwA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Ddwmz0vxLJwA&d=VBfUe0L1U1Z5uIZsl0533jOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=17fb182b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dwmz0vxLJwA</a><br />\n<br />\n呢首咁正既歌中文版搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人可以從新改過d中文歌詞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xa8n8KuRNv8&amp;t=6s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dxa8n8KuRNv8%26t%3D6s&d=VBfUe0L1U1Z5uIZsl0533jOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=6b724c1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xa8n8KuRNv8&amp;t=6s</a><br />\nBGM<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ilyricsbuzz.com/2018/02/akira-kushida-kyukyoku-no-seisen.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Filyricsbuzz.com%2F2018%2F02%2Fakira-kushida-kyukyoku-no-seisen.html&d=VBfUe0L1U1Z5uIZsl0533jOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=ae9f42d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ilyricsbuzz.com/2018/02/akira-kushida-kyukyoku-no-seisen.html</a><br />\n究極の聖戦 バトル<br />\n日文主唱 串田アキラ<br />\n<br />\nカカカカ勝ちだぜ<br />\nグングングングン群を抜き<br />\nジャンジャンビャンビャン究極の聖戦（バトル）<br />\n<br />\n意味はないさ 戦うだけ<br />\n出会えて嬉しいぜ すげえやつに<br />\n教えてくれるかい？ 俺の強さを<br />\n<br />\nパワー全開 限界突破<br />\nこっから先は 神もただポカンさ<br />\n<br />\nカカカカ勝ちだぜ<br />\nグングングングン群を抜き<br />\nジャンジャンビャンビャン究極の聖戦（バトル）<br />\n<br />\nママママまじかよ<br />\nテンテンテンテン天も地も<br />\nジャンジャンビャンビャン火柱に溶る<br />\n意味はないさ 戦うだけさ<br />\nやがて自我が無になるまで<br />\n<br />\n拳が逸れる度 空が割れる<br />\nすべてを壊したら 何が生まれる？<br />\n一撃必殺 一千万回<br />\n身体ズタボロ どこで止めりゃいいの？<br />\n<br />\nカカカカ勝ちだぜ<br />\nグングングングン群を抜き<br />\nジャンジャンビャンビャン究極の聖戦（バトル）<br />\n<br />\nバババババカだね<br />\nザンザンザンザン残酷な<br />\nジャンジャンビャンビャン宿命を笑え<br />\n元気玉が漲る限り<br />\n光放て 永遠まで<br />\n<br />\n存在覚醒 限界再生<br />\n意識を超えて 戦いは続く<br />\n<br />\nママママまじかよ<br />\nテンテンテンテン天も地も<br />\nジャンジャンビャンビャン火柱に溶る<br />\n<br />\nカカカカ勝ちだぜ<br />\nグングングングン群を抜き<br />\nジャンジャンビャンビャン究極の聖戦（バトル）<br />\n<br />\nバババババカだね<br />\nザンザンザンザン残酷な<br />\nジャンジャンビャンビャン宿命を笑え<br />\n意味はないさ 戦うだけさ<br />\nやがて自我が無になるまで"},{"pid":"e67471ecf751b702dd3368a6f3ba352dae1c4f20","tid":732032,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:37:52.000Z","msg":"黃霑唱先唱神粹"},{"pid":"642e8559b7e16bc990fb04debbedce934a3e1d8f","tid":732032,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e67471ecf751b702dd3368a6f3ba352dae1c4f20","tid":732032,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:37:52.000Z","msg":"黃霑唱先唱神粹"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:44:25.000Z","msg":"有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114d37b4671b4c4883dbf96a466a7b4f0f545203","tid":732032,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:46:09.000Z","msg":"佢鳩改咋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港冇官方"},{"pid":"93eaf4af07e06268368da05282cf91a905aa3318","tid":732032,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"114d37b4671b4c4883dbf96a466a7b4f0f545203","tid":732032,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:46:09.